data.text:
Congratulations to all students on the President’s and Dean’s Lists for your diligent work and academic accomplishments this semester. Keep it up!

Please contact the Office of the Registrar for any questions regarding the President’s or Dean’s lists at (603) 535-2345 or psu-registrar@plymouth.edu.

President’s List

To be named to the President’s List, a student must achieve a grade point average of 3.7 or better for the spring semester and must have attempted at least 12 credit hours during the semester.
